name: Martial God Regressed to Level 2
author: Yeombi
content: [NO. 4212: &#039Humanity&#039 has failed the Demotion Match.][NO. 4212: ‘Humanity’ has been deemed useless. Beginning deletion.]Earth lost the fight for survival in the BattleNet system and humanity now faces eradication. However, Jihan Seong is given another chance. He has returned three years into the past before BattleNet became a life-or-death game.With his knowledge of the future, he’s determined to become the strongest player. Will Jihan be able to change the fate of humanity? And more imp
